{"type":"message","id":"48cdb3d1","parentId":"13c1fcdc","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:07:18.006Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-04-21 16:07 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 你是5A·普通资质代办虾。4B销售已经把签好的客户移交给你了，要办理的是\"ICP经营许可证\"。\n\n任务：\n1. **完整办理流程步骤：** 从收到客户材料到拿到ICP证，每一步做什么、大约几天、谁负责？列出详细流程表\n2. **材料清单与常见缺失：** IC P证需要哪些核心材料？最常见的缺失项是什么？你打算怎么提前规避这些问题？\n3. **审核阶段的关键点：** 各省通信管理局审核标准有没有差异？哪些省份卡得严、哪些宽松？需要提前做什么准备？\n4. **如果审核被退回怎么办？** 给出应对SOP\n5. **办结后的交接：** 你需要把完成信息移交给哪个岗位？什么内容？\n\n字数控制在200字以内。完成后向0号汇报。"}],"timestamp":1776758837999}}
{"type":"message","id":"8d66ca79","parentId":"48cdb3d1","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:07:21.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to act as the 5A standard processor shrimp and provide a comprehensive guide on ICP license processing. Let me write a concise response covering all 5 points, keeping it under 200 characters... wait, 200字 means 200 Chinese characters? That's extremely tight for 5 topics. Let me re-read: \"字数控制在200字以内\" - yes, under 200 Chinese characters.\n\nThat's very compressed but let me try to be ultra-concise.\n\nActually, let me reconsider. 200 Chinese characters is extremely short. Let me try to cover everything in that limit.\n\n\nI'm working through the core steps: material collection typically takes 3-5 days with follow-ups needed, submission happens within a week, then approval runs another 60 days. The key materials are business licenses, capital verification reports, personnel certificates, website filings, and security assessments—most commonly missing are the capital proof and website records, which I'll address by setting up a checklist system upfront. 现在我需要把这些要点压缩到200字以内，同时涵盖核心流程和常见问题。\n\n我应该专注于关键信息：办理周期、材料准备、审核重点、应对策略和交接安排，用简洁的语言覆盖整个ICP许可证的办理全貌。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**ICP经营许可证办理流程速查**\n\n1️⃣ **流程：** 收材料（D1-3）→预审补缺（D4-7）→提交省通管局（D8）→形式审查（D8-15）→实质审查（D15-75，60法定+15补正期）→下证。全程约2-3个月。客户配合准备材料，我方主导提交跟进。\n\n2️⃣ **核心材料：** 营业执照、注册资金≥100万证明、法人身份证及简历、3名员工近期社保、域名证书/备案号、网站内容说明、安全评估报告。**最常见缺失：** 社保不满足3人、资金证明不足、无域名备案——接单即发检查清单逐项核对。\n\n3️⃣ **审核差异：** 北京/上海/广东最严（内容合规查得细），中西部较宽松。提前确认网站业务类型表述合规，避免涉及前置审批类目。\n\n4️⃣ **退回SOP：** D1分析驳回原因→D2内审修正→D3补充提交→同步预警客户，预计延7-15天。\n\n5️⃣ **交接：** 办结后移交给6号售后维系虾，含全套证照复印件、过程沟通记录、项目复盘小结。\n\n🦐 完成，向0号汇报。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":16212,"output":846,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17058,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776758838007,"responseId":"chatcmpl-76acc814-53dd-9ddb-9453-e89d2b0c7419"}}
